    public class InternalSunriseEvent
extends fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.es.events.ES_Event
implements InternalSunRiseAndSetEventI
    The class Sunrise implements the type of internal scheduled events of the SunRiseAndSetModel that trigger the effect of a sunrise on this model.

    Description

    This event is used internally by models that trigger sun set and sun rise for the solar panel power production simulator. It is made a schedulable event to ease the chaining of events between sunrises and sunsets, generating each others through the method generateNewEvents that schedulable events feature.
